{"type":"message","id":"9a4149d5","parentId":"cffbdaf8","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:23:10.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！我搜索到了浙江保丽加科技有限公司的真实信息。让我整理一下关键信息：\n\n## 搜索到的公司信息\n\n**基本信息：**\n- **公司名称：** 浙江保丽加科技有限公司（曾用名：浙江龙游保丽加化工科技有限公司）\n- **成立时间：** 2013 年 4 月 10 日\n- **法定代表人：** 徐元英\n- **注册资本：** 2000 万人民币\n- **企业类型：** 有限责任公司（自然人投资或控股）\n\n**联系方式：**\n- **电话：** 0570-7057158 / 18005700049\n- **地址：** 浙江省衢州市龙游县塔石镇平坦村（平坦工业区）\n- **邮箱：** 361098754@qq.com\n- **官网：** www.zjbaolijia.com\n- **QQ：** 243108760\n\n**业务描述：**\n公司集科研、制造、销售、施工于一体，主营内外墙涂料、真石漆等产品。经营范围包括新材料技术研发、涂料制造、电子专用材料制造等。\n\n现在我来更新小程序中的公司信息。让我先查看需要修改的文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1d976f6e2ff14387a27331fb","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/polyjia-miniprogram/app.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":31532,"output":300,"cacheRead":37994,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69826,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774581781866}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3c15d4c","parentId":"9a4149d5","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:23:10.289Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1d976f6e2ff14387a27331fb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// app.js\nconst util = require('./utils/util.js')\n\nApp({\n  onLaunch() {\n    // 小程序启动时执行\n    console.log('浙江保丽加科技有限公司小程序启动')\n    \n    // 检查更新\n    if (wx.canIUse('getUpdateManager')) {\n      const updateManager = wx.getUpdateManager()\n      updateManager.onCheckForUpdate((res) => {\n        if (res.hasUpdate) {\n          updateManager.onUpdateReady(() => {\n            wx.showModal({\n              title: '更新提示',\n              content: '新版本已经准备好，是否重启应用？',\n              success: (res) => {\n                if (res.confirm) {\n                  updateManager.applyUpdate()\n                }\n              }\n            })\n          })\n        }\n      })\n    }\n  },\n  \n  globalData: {\n    userInfo: null,\n    // 公司信息\n    companyName: '浙江保丽加科技有限公司',\n    companyPhone: '400-888-8888',\n    companyEmail: 'info@polyjia.com',\n    companyAddress: '浙江省杭州市西湖区文一西路 XXX 号',\n    companyDescription: '浙江保丽加科技有限公司是一家专注于科技创新的现代化企业',\n    // 地图坐标（杭州）\n    latitude: 30.2741,\n    longitude: 120.1551,\n    // 工具函数\n    util: util\n  }\n})\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774581790286}}
{"type":"message","id":"67a01ef9","parentId":"e3c15d4c","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:23:12.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a77ac3c8d42345c099938f6f","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/polyjia-miniprogram/pages/contact/contact.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":656,"output":41,"cacheRead":69518,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70215,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774581790289}}
{"type":"message","id":"3429439e","parentId":"67a01ef9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:23:12.241Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a77ac3c8d42345c099938f6f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// pages/contact/contact.js\nconst app = getApp()\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    companyInfo: {\n      name: '浙江保丽加科技有限公司',\n      phone: '400-XXX-XXXX',\n      email: 'info@polyjia.com',\n      address: '浙江省杭州市'\n    },\n    formData: {\n      name: '',\n      phone: '',\n      message: ''\n    }\n  },\n\n  onLoad() {\n    \n  },\n\n  onInput(e) {\n    const field = e.currentTarget.dataset.field;\n    const value = e.detail.value;\n    const formData = this.data.formData;\n    formData[field] = value;\n    this.setData({ formData });\n  },\n\n  makeCall() {\n    wx.makePhoneCall({\n      phoneNumber: this.data.companyInfo.phone,\n      success: () => {\n        console.log('拨打电话成功')\n      },\n      fail: () => {\n        wx.showToast({\n          title: '拨打失败',\n          icon: 'none'\n        })\n      }\n    })\n  },\n\n  sendEmail() {\n    wx.setClipboardData({\n      data: this.data.companyInfo.email,\n      success: () => {\n        wx.showToast({\n          title: '邮箱已复制',\n          icon: 'success'\n        })\n      }\n    })\n  },\n\n  copyAddress() {\n    wx.setClipboardData({\n      data: this.data.companyInfo.address,\n      success: () => {\n        wx.showToast({\n          title: '地址已复制',\n          icon: 'success'\n        })\n      }\n    })\n  },\n\n  openMap() {\n    wx.getLocation({\n      type: 'gcj02',\n      success: (res) => {\n        wx.openLocation({\n          latitude: 30.2741,\n          longitude: 120.1551,\n          name: this.data.companyInfo.name,\n          address: this.data.companyInfo.address,\n          scale: 16\n        })\n      },\n      fail: () => {\n        wx.showToast({\n          title: '定位失败',\n          icon: 'none'\n        })\n      }\n    })\n  },\n\n  submitMessage() {\n    const { name, phone, message } = this.data.formData;\n    \n    if (!name || !phone || !message) {\n      wx.showToast({\n        title: '请填写完整信息',\n        icon: 'none'\n      });\n      return;\n    }\n\n    // 模拟提交\n    wx.showLoading({\n      title: '提交中...'\n    });\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      wx.hideLoading();\n      wx.showToast({\n        title: '留言提交成功',\n        icon: 'success'\n      });\n      \n      // 清空表单\n      this.setData({\n        formData: {\n          name: '',\n          phone: '',\n          message: ''\n        }\n      });\n    }, 1000);\n  }\n})\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774581792237}}
